CoD servers management.

cli - Old python command-line only script.

codadmin - new Webui based on Django

------------
    DOC
------------

https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/1.3/

------------
Requirements
------------
Django 1.3
SQLite 3
python-psutil /* Will be removed shortly */

------------
DEVELOPEMENT
------------

Install django libs on ubuntu 11.10:

  sudo aptitude install python-django sqlite3 python-psutil

Clone repository
   git clone http://github.com/cheuveulu/LANBox.git
Got to codadmin folder
   cd LANBox/codadmin

* First time :
   python manage.py syncdb

Run web server
   python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000


--------------
Usage
--------------
Status - Main page
http://localhost:8000/

Admin url
http://localhost:8000/admin


Happy hacking
